token_lists.title: MSRI-WHITE Components
token_lists.description: V4w.enko - "MSRI-WHITE-..." series is "Most Strange Rainbow Inside" on White background. An algorithm developed by v4w.enko with "voronoi diagram" in 3d usage together with "loft strings". The "Loft Strings" are the re-parametrized lines whose geometry depends on special harmonic chords and operates with the "voronoi" cells. Dedicated to the "strings theory" and "wave universe" cosmology.
